review_detailed_main:
I didn't know what to expect when I started watching, the movie had such low rating. To me this movie was really good, it hold all the good aspects for a post apocalyptic movies think it's really unfair to rate it so low as 5-6 stars when other movies that are total crap gets 8-9. It's exciting and you wonder what's gonna happen next. I'm not a movie critic nor a film expert, but for me this was a pleasure to watch. The actors play their roles well, it's feels like this is how it would be if this disaster happened. I can't say that I wasn't a little bummed at the end, but still it also keeps you wondering and I guess that's how they intended it to be.

If you like these kind of movies you won't be disappointed!

//cheers
